      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine runs consistently, and the transmission shifts through all gears, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several cosmetic blemishes, including paint fading on the hood, a few door dings, and some surface rust starting on the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpet. All major electronics work, though the AC takes a few minutes to get cold. It is a solid, functional car that would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and routine maintenance.",
