    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This driver\u2019s example has had the critical subframe reinforcement completed and the dual-VANOS system serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The chassis remains sharp with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a limited-slip differential that provides excellent power transfer out of apexes. While the paint shows light patina indicative of its 'good' status, the internal vitals are strong, boasting consistent compression across all cylinders and a cooling system recently refreshed with a high-flow water pump. A purist-spec machine optimized for throttle response and longitudinal grip.",
